<p>As mentioned above, Global journalists (who will be clearly identified as such) will also contribute material to the Forums in order to stimulate discussions and ensure the smooth running of the Forums. The Forums may also contain User Generated Content from special guests selected by Global. The opinions of those Global journalists and special guests are their own and are not necessarily endorsed by Global. They should not be considered by you as professional advisers and any comments they make are not intended to amount to advice on which reliance should be placed.</p>
